        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A short energy statement for the decision to be the person who changes the family money pattern. The release acknowledges the inherited struggle; the allow names what comes next.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how energy statements work",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
